Zero entry doorways. Private patio in the back. Energy efficient home! Option to build 10x14 storage room above garage.

For sale: $455,000. Welcome to 13423 Carlingford Lane.  You'll fall in love with this beautiful home and love the 3 car tandem garage.  Upon entering you'll find gorgeous hardwood floors, an attractive layout, mudroom and walk-in pantry.  The kitchen offers granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances and a large center island with seating.  You'll love the two gas fireplaces, updated lighting and terrific storage.  Upstairs is 4 bedrooms, upper level laundry, large loft and office (could be upper 5th bedroom) with French doors.  New washer and dryer 2018.  New dishwasher Oct 2019. Range, fridge and microwave new in 2016.  New roof 2017. The utility room offers great additional storage or workout space.  This  neighborhood features walking trails, 2 pools and playground area. The garage is a three stall with a tandem third stall and high ceilings.

For sale: $229,900. Updated from top to bottom, 2 BR plus den, 2 BA first floor unit, 9 foot ceilings, 2 garage parking spaces, close to elevator, rarely does this type of property become available for sale. Located in a secluded enclave of 55+ condos, vibrant senior community in a desirable Rosemount locale. Condo features all new carpet, vinyl plank flooring, kitchen appliances, backsplash & kitchen hardware, vanity & shower door in master bath, toilets, entire unit repainted. Pleasing open lay out, kitchen is open to living room & walks out to oversized patio overlooking green space; private master suite, laundry in unit w/newer washer & dryer. High demand Bards Crossing complex offers many amenities inc. party room w/kitchen & deck, craft room, library, exercise room, heated underground parking w/car wash, woodworking workshop, storage lockers, guest room rents for $40/night, well run assoc; 3 elevators in bldg condo is located in. Great opportunity for those looking for a move in ready unit.

For sale: $1,150,000. HOME IS OCCUPIED - PLEASE SET UP APPOINTMENT BEFORE ACCESSING THE PROPERTY:
A gorgeous, unique country estate on over five acres!  Amazing quality and distinctive design is apparent everywhere.  Four bedrooms and four baths plus a stunning MIL suite on the main level. A barrel ceiling Sun Room and fifty feet of maintenance free deck show cases the private yard and wooded privacy. The gourmet kitchen is stunning with custom cabinetry, a vegetable sink, side by side double refrigerator/freezer, wine refrigerator, double oven, a matching custom hutch, panoramic views of the yard and much more. Every room has a walkout to the massive deck as nature was carefully incorporated into the design and layout. The immense garage space is impressive with two tandem garages, one at 44x34 and one at 40x24 with room for 8 cars plus additional parking and a pad for a large trailer or boat. The exteriors are artfully designed with interesting articulation and mixed elements of brick, stone and siding.

description:
Recently sold: $240,000. Beautifully maintained 2-level townhome in the highly desired Harmony Village Neighborhood. This home features 3 bedrooms and 2 1/2 baths. The half bath is located perfectly on the main level adjacent to the kitchen and coat closet. Additionally on the main level, you have an updated kitchen, dining and living rooms. Upstairs, you?ll find another living or family room, the master bedroom which is very spacious and includes a full bath with both a walk in shower and jetted tub, and a walk in closet. The other two bedrooms are also well sized, and are on the opposite side of the house, ensuring some additional space for the master. Lastly upstairs, there is yet another full bathroom and the washer and dryer closet. The home also has a great two car garage, measuring 17 1/2 ft wide and 23ft deep. It has been finished with painted walls, 6 new LED light strips and enough ceiling storage to store over 35 standard size totes!

The location and neighborhood offer many ammenities, including the shared Harmony Village pool, gym and community room.These are all 1 block away. There is a city park, shelter, baseball field and basketball court adjacent to the community pool. At the SW corner of the neighborhood, there is also a frisbee golf course.  If you like to walk, bike or run, there are two great city trails that border the north and south side of the neighborhood, one on Connemara Trail and the other on Biscayne Avenue.

Come see your next home!
